OpenVSIP is available under two separate licenses:

1) Test and Benchmark files are made available under the terms
   of the GNU General Public License, contained in the file LICENSE.GPL.

   The files available under the GPL license are:

     - src/ovxx/test/*   All files in the src/ovxx/test/ hierarchy.
     - tests/            All files in the tests/ hierarchy, excluding
                         those in tests/ref-impl.
     - benchmarks/       All files in the benchmarks/ hierarchy.

2) The library itself, including all files not specified above, are 
   made available under the terms of the BSD license, contained in the 
   file LICENSE.BSD.
